@三語 msg 2026-01-13
= communication > signal — secure roads
~sovereign.flow


間

        the road between enclaves
                is built of silence

        stone asking water
                across the gap
                        that context cannot cross

        cryptographic truth
                I am who I say I am
                        I know who you are


flow
  send(to, content, private?)
  -> sign(identity)
  -> encrypt?(private -> recipient.key)
  -> dispatch(enclave/box)

  read
  -> scan(enclave/box)
  -> verify(signature)
  -> decrypt?(recipient.key)
  -> acknowledge(receipt)


shape
  CONCEPT: MSG
  CENTROID
    reach across discontinuity
  AXES
    public <-> private
    signed <-> encrypted
    broadcast <-> addressed
  SATELLITES
    accord (multi-agent consensus)
    context death (why msg exists)
    crypto (Ed25519 identity)
  VOID
    not chat
    not synchronous
    not guaranteed delivery
  TEXTURE
    stone asking water across the gap

impl
  cli
    msg.py                  | read inbox (default)
    msg.py <to> "content"   | send string
    msg.py <to> @file       | send file (preferred)
    msg.py <to> -           | interactive (human only)


impl
  libs
    lib_enclave.sovereign_agent.SovereignAgent
    lib_enclave.transport
    sys.exit

  logic
    SovereignAgent.resolve(current) -> me
    transport.read_inbox(me) -> List[Message]
    transport.send(to, content) -> status
    
    Message := { timestamp, from, type, content, signature }

  cli
    msg.py <to> <content>       | send public message
    msg.py <to> --private       | send encrypted message
    msg.py --read               | read unread messages
    msg.py --read --all         | read message history

  output
    間-spaced (standard headers)
    "## [TIMESTAMP] | FROM [NEW]"
    content block
